  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the destruction of the world caused by ww3 and Ai, The Galactic Federations declares   earth a radioactive wasteland and open to PvP. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Synthians are a race dedicated to build and regrow life in destroyed planets, your mission is to clean the city and survive, basically a really hard waste collection Job, the more you clean the more money you make. This is the first game that i make so thats why its free :) . Runs on the steamdeck</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboard: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lets clean and chill :D</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333840/extras/b62fa2b038d4555374c3a177edaec37d.avif?t=1763981638\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pulse gun upgrades: discover the secret upgrades and new firing modes for your gun .</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Energy chargers:</strong> Replenish the energy of your gun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333840/extras/b541341fd16ddce9ec35f19927e28ca3.avif?t=1763981638\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Activate the cleaners to clean the air of the city and stop the enemy aliens.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333840/extras/4ecfe0cee554bfb4d315bff5b2b8021c.avif?t=1763981638\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333840/extras/11bc7e01e9867485727ecf7dec02e9e4.avif?t=1763981638\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333840/extras_big/11bc7e01e9867485727ecf7dec02e9e4.webp?t=1763981638 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The leaderboard</strong>: you can check the leaderboard at   or in the royal plaza inside the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the destruction of the world caused by ww3 and Ai, The Galactic Federations declares   earth a radioactive wasteland and open to PvP. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Synthians are a race dedicated to build and regrow life in destroyed planets, your mission is to clean the city and survive, basically a really hard waste collection Job, the more you clean the more money you make. This is the first game that i make so thats why its free :) . Runs on the steamdeck</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboard: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lets clean and chill :D</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333840/extras/b62fa2b038d4555374c3a177edaec37d.avif?t=1763981638\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pulse gun upgrades: discover the secret upgrades and new firing modes for your gun .</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Energy chargers:</strong> Replenish the energy of your gun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333840/extras/b541341fd16ddce9ec35f19927e28ca3.avif?t=1763981638\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Activate the cleaners to clean the air of the city and stop the enemy aliens.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333840/extras/4ecfe0cee554bfb4d315bff5b2b8021c.avif?t=1763981638\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p